import "./Description.scss"; const Description = () => { return (

About This Service

*Want a 45-mins sample session? Message me for a $10 Custom Offer*

IMPORTANT: The longer you work with me the better results you can expect

With 4 sessions you WILL see how to become a better version of yourself. But do you think your life can change in just 4 weeks?

That’s not how it works. The process of transformation takes time, period.

If you are TRULY committed to becoming the PEAK version of yourself… Then it’s a no brainer:

Either subscribe for 3 or 6 months (Subscribe To Save button is located under the price)

The more committed you are to yourself the longer you should subscribe to your favorite package.

If you order the Premium package and subscribe for 6 months, you can become a whole different person by the end of it.

All I need from you is commitment, patience, dedication & consistency. If you are coachable, I will guide you exactly where you need to go to.

But YOU are the one who must take the path I guide you towards. I’m “just” your guide who can get you to your goals faster

If you’re ready to start your REAL journey, take that first step now by ordering what best fits your needs!

PS: Before you order, please read the rules pdf! (gig pictures)

Coaching catagory

Personal growth

Coach's gender

Male

); }; export default Description;
